snippet.title: Moonlit OST Track 1 ~ Engines area (upper)
snippet.description:
♫♫-
A song from my game Moonlit
The game was made for a game jam, you can download it here:
https://zahranworrell.itch.io/moonlit

Purchase the soundtrack on bandcamp:
https://zahranworrell.bandcamp.com/album/moonlit-ost

Arranged and composed by Zahran Worrell
Cover art by King Worrell (https://twitter.com/King_Worrell)
Made with Pxtone Collage and Pxtone Collab using samples by Nifflas, Peposoft, Kiriyama, Studio Pixel, ArcOfDream and 𝖂𝖎𝖑𝖑𝕿𝖍𝖚𝖗
The soundtrack was very much inspired by old games such as Knytt Stories and Cave Story
Special thanks to Yuxshao for making Pxtone Collab and Canana for feedback and suggestions
